channel.title: Adding "Silab Items"
channel.description:
Hey, now then, I have a 317 client but want to add the "Silab items" to it. Cache update right? Skillcapes, Godswords etc.
So I was wondering if anyone would be so nice as to explain how I go about adding the new cache etc. to my 317. My server is apparently already compatible, but there's obviously something wrong because when I spawn above 9,000, it's seeds, nulls and dwarf heads.
I know this is a common problem but I don't know what's behind it all.
I'm a beginner.
I'm willing to learn, so give me the best information you got please and that will do fine. Even a link to a tutorial would be good.
Cheers.
